<span style=\"color: red;\">有人向現場噴高濃度胡椒水，在場既人包括記者都狂咳</span></span>,之後個阿叔就俾人拉左出車，然後<span style=\"color: red;\">又再黎一次高濃度胡椒水</span>在場人士又一次狂咳，蘋果記者咳到cam到扭轉左，一回頭既畫面就係，個阿伯已經成面係血<br />\n<br />\n順帶一提有人話現場見到機場果日條金毛j"},{"pid":"ee0d134f08d3115b66c05bae7ea32a80a8767868","tid":1585720,"uid":312526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T17:16:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dd525819efbdbb9bbe832568e402f63a28d6d140","tid":1585720,"uid":44916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"159f23d0646b37dea364cf1de91cbd91cbaecf37","tid":1585720,"uid":220690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ccea5b10ec2cc9d8f8f9f9d2e236f4679c29a370","tid":1585720,"uid":44916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ed0f28441301003ea55c088a99ccee92ab67feb6","tid":1585720,"uid":181462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T17:06:57.000Z","msg":"好似話有兩單，呢個第一單冇問題，出事俾記者影哂好似係另一單"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T17:07:39.000Z","msg":"上的士個阿伯？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T17:14:21.000Z","msg":"YES"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T17:26:06.000Z","msg":"嗰單就真係唔知起因，最後被個無戴口罩嘅爆頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e79dfbb031630ef856f7bc3ac442f57044de8610","tid":1585720,"uid":72065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T17:33:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aff3b9f73699c875bfb04b839016a276db1171e4","tid":1585720,"uid":271729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T17:34:23.000Z","msg":"睇嚟又係班死黑警攪事,班冚家剷無惡不作"},{"pid":"1f81d05d6146cc80d94e91a0ebf69f990c28d185","tid":1585720,"uid":306664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T17:34:55.000Z","msg":"唔好再用'私鳥'<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dec525bb27ea706da85e896f4f6a80fd6d3aeed1","tid":1585720,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T17:3